{"tid":1996168,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國外交部駐港公署強烈譴責美國政客大放厥詞","createTime":"2020-04-30T19:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T20:33:18.000Z","uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"882aaf87c444f6edb7b8ff131b484b6aa258af98","tid":1996168,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T19:23:24.000Z","msg":"外交部駐港公署不點名批評美國國務卿蓬佩奧再度評論香港情況，強烈譴責和堅決反對美國有關政客對香港事務喋喋不休、大放厥詞。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧早前說，華府持續關注北京干預香港管治，又表明反對香港就23條立法。<br />\n<br />\n外交部駐港公署發言人強調，維護國家安全是全面準確貫徹「一國兩制」方針的核心要求，是香港特區根據基本法必須履行的憲制責任，也是確保香港長治久安的根本保障。美國政客信口雌黃、造謠污蔑，<strong>再次暴露他們根深蒂固的破壞「一國兩制」、搞亂香港、進而利用香港對中國內地進行滲透破壞分裂顛覆、遏制中國發展的險惡用心。但這是癡心妄想，不自量力，必將遭到可恥的失敗。<br />\n</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523688-20200501.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523688-20200501.htm&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rCWBhM8hN5wqk8YifI4Fu34%3D&h=3083866e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523688-20200501.htm&h=11becb5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523688-20200501.htm</a>"},{"pid":"593a7dd8d8d3a344521e6b3380ffedc419acc056","tid":1996168,"uid":125193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T19:23:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">這是癡心妄想，不自量力，必將遭到可恥的失敗。</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33071185d1389d6c70fd3acba0cda13d99134e2","tid":1996168,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T19:25:32.000Z","msg":"好多四字詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56324e6e6fb470d7c62ce47aa4ba69d8f28d5f17","tid":19961